abilities.name: Sturdy
abilities.description: After using 'Moves' that make it fall asleep or paralyzed, it doesn't fall in battle.

abilities.name: Unaware
abilities.description: Your opponent's stat changes affect your Pokémon as if you had no Status condition.

tutorMoves.name: Lock-On
tutorMoves.description: Makes its target an ally, making the Pokémon's moves bounce off it.
